dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Map shows by color coding : Arab, Greek, Turkey with Armenian and Kurdish territories, British Protectorate and Mandate, French Mandate, Arab territory, Greek territory, railways open and under construction, scenes of battles, tracks, canals, steamer routes with distances in nautical miles. Includes inset map: Turkey 1914, scale approximately 1:25,344,000. Copyright "Geographia" Ltd.
